{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/H1.png?t=1732798010\" /><br>Project Adrenaline takes the classic arena shooter formula and infuses it with modern, high-octane mechanics.<br>Each player is a soon-to-be corpse in the arena of neon-gladiators. Born to die in glorious combat, you must parkour and kill your way to ultimate victory as the crowd cheers you on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/Clip2.gif?t=1732798010\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/Clip4.gif?t=1732798010\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/H2.png?t=1732798010\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>32+ Player</strong> Skull-Crushing Chaos<br></li><li>Blood Pumping <strong>Parkour Mechanics</strong><br></li><li>Frequent Rotation of <strong>New Game Modes</strong><br></li><li>Constant <strong>Map Updates</strong><br></li><li>Wide Selection of <strong>Deployable Abilities</strong><br></li><li><i><strong>SO MUCH MORE!</strong></i></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/H3.png?t=1732798010\" /><br>Project Adrenaline is still <strong>very </strong>early in development. Our ultimate goal is to bring arena shooters to more modern players. This means modernizing certain mechanics and adjusting the game to satisfy players. Project Adrenaline is yours to mold into the arena shooter of your dreams. We are eager to hear your feedback, criticisms and ideas!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971120/extras/BMWE_SteamStore-Small-01.png?t=1732798010\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app